### Start paper verification code expiry (720 days)
POST http://localhost:4015/v1/paper-verification-code/expire
Authorization: AWS4-HMAC-SHA256 securesecretstring
Accept: application/vnd.opg-data.v1+json,application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "P-1234-1234-1234-12",
  "expiry_reason": "first_time_use"
}

### Convert paper verification code to digital (30 days)
POST http://localhost:4015/v1/paper-verification-code/expire
Authorization: AWS4-HMAC-SHA256 securesecretstring
Accept: application/vnd.opg-data.v1+json,application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "P-1234-1234-1234-12",
  "expiry_reason": "paper_to_digital"
}
